@model Blue.Cosacs.Web.Areas.Warehouse.Models.Driver
<tr data-id="@Model.Id" class="edit">
@if (Html.HasPermission(Blue.Cosacs.Warehouse.Common.WarehousePermissionEnum.DriverMaintenanceEdit))
 {
    <td class="actions"></td>
 }
    <td colspan="2">
        @using (Html.BeginForm("RecordEdit", "Drivers", FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "form-horizontal" }))
        {
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="Name" class="col col-lg-3 control-label">Name</label>
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.Name, new { @class="form-control form-horizontal" })
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="PhoneNumber" class="col col-lg-3 control-label">Phone</label>
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.PhoneNumber, new { @class="form-control form-horizontal" })
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="text-warning">In order to add to a truck any new Driver created, you need to log out and log in again.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        }
    </td>
</tr>